tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE education_partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_name VARCHAR(255),
    partner_country VARCHAR(100),
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
    collaboration_focus TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(100),
    country VARCHAR(50),
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    university_name VARCHAR(100),
    contact_person VARCHAR(100),
    collaboration_description TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnerships(id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnership (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
    partnership_location VARCHAR(100),
    established_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaboration (
    collab_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    collab_description TEXT,
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE contact (
    contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_name VARCHAR(100),
    contact_email VARCHAR(50),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(100),
    partner_country VARCHAR(50),
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    collaboration_name VARCHAR(100),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE academic_institutions (
    institution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    institution_name VARCHAR(100),
    country VARCHAR(50),
    website VARCHAR(100),
    establishment_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE partnership_contacts (
    contact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    contact_name VARCHAR(100),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    role VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (partnership_id) REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_country VARCHAR(50),
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
    agreement_date DATE,
    collaboration_purpose TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE universities (
    university_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    university_name VARCHAR(100),
    country VARCHAR(50),
    established_date DATE,
    website_url VARCHAR(200)
);

CREATE TABLE programs (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(100),
    university_id INT REFERENCES universities(university_id),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE courses (
    course_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    course_name VARCHAR(100),
    program_id INT REFERENCES programs(program_id),
    course_type VARCHAR(50),
    credit_hours INT
);

CREATE TABLE instructors (
    instructor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    instructor_name VARCHAR(100),
    course_id INT REFERENCES courses(course_id),
    specialization VARCHAR(100),
    email VARCHAR(100)
);
